<head>大正 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0476003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0476003">不分卷，〔佛…譯〕五十九字－【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0476004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0476004">於＝于【明】下同</note>
<note n="0477001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0477001">抹＝末【明】</note>
<note n="0477002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0477002"><g ref="#CB01464">㙠</g>＝翳【三】，醫【宮】</note>
